message.body: I heard back from Pete this morning! Thank you for all the love! Junior production?
Hoooooray!!!!!!
I talked to him on the phone yesterday. Awesome.
Wow you're so great ! I'm so grateful. Are you also teaching that?
I'm teaching editing, creative practices (2 sections) and vid prod. As far as I know. What day are you in?
You are making bank!! I have to decide which section but likely Thursdays and Fridays?
So let me make you dinner this week?
Yay! I'll be in campus on Thursday so we get lunch or drinks after class!
Can you do Saturday or Sunday dinner this week? I have my 90s rock concert and shooting in bucks county Tuesday and Thursday
Or tonight??
I want to hear all about it! (Shooting ..) maybe tonight? I have garden day 4-8 or so, just my grill back- maybe yea??!!
Tonight at 8 is that what yr saying ha!
Not too late!
Cata is still in NYC so this is an intimate dinner girl.
Also please tell me the food you hate
Eggplant I'm thinking
And corn and salad of some kind
Great!! I am sick of mushrooms but I'll still eat them ha! I can bring vodka sodas and some things to grill. Like veggie dogs.
That's awesome.
Sounds perfect. I will see you at 8!
Also beets-
Should I pick any of the veggies up from the co op or do you have these?
I have candy beets and leeks eggplant and greens - I'll prob have more stuff after garden day!
OMG this sounds so good
Um. Do you remember how to BBQ?
A hahaha. Lol. We need charcoal you got that?
I think you light that on fire with lighter fluid and let it get hot til the coals are red?
Lol
You are killing me!
No it's cool. I have that stuff! I realiZe I don't actually have grill tools?! Like a flipper and a grabber- duh. And all this nice food
I have those! I will bring them!
Phew! I'm going to marinate the eggplant! And start this scary fire soon
Yayayay! I'm leaving here in about 20! I'll see you soon!
Xo
Here!!!
